Mint Fox is here to help you activate your new Mint Mobile account and transfer your existing phone number to it. Don't worry, it's easy as f@#! (we said "fox") ... 1. Get your old account number, zip code and password from your previous wirelesss carrier

2. Go to mintmobile.com and click on 'Activate' in the top right corner

3. Enter the 11-digit activation code located on the back of the SIM card in the upper right hand corner

4. Select 'Transfer an Existing Number' and enter your account number and password from your old phone company

5. Voilà! Most numbers will transfer over within minutes, but some may take up to 24 hours

If you have any questions about the status of your number please contact support@mintmobile.com or +1-213-372-7777
